{"tid":147440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【廢老禍港】外地傳入H7N9個案增至五宗","createTime":"2017-03-08T00:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T00:02:39.000Z","uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"489188fe69ead3314345b7d8d40f7cf691c984ee","tid":147440,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T00:01:39.000Z","msg":"外地傳入H7N9個案增至五宗<br />\n<br />\n2017年03月07日<br />\n衞生防護中心公布，76歲老翁確診感染甲型禽流感（H7N9），為本港入冬以來第五宗外地傳入個案。<br />\n <br />\n老翁為長期病患者，2月11日至3月1日逗留福建福州，其間到過街市。他上周五發燒、咳嗽帶痰，翌日到私家診所求診，本月5日往仁濟醫院急症室求醫，現已轉送瑪嘉烈醫院接受隔離治療，情況危殆。<br />\n <br />\n其密切接觸者至今沒有病徵，正接受醫學監察。<br />\n <br />\n防護中心呼籲市民在本地或外遊時保持個人、食物和環境衞生。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.news.gov.hk/tc/categories/health/html/2017/03/20170307_220138.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcategories%2Fhealth%2Fhtml%2F2017%2F03%2F20170307_220138.shtml&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=90a2b2d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.news.gov.hk/tc/categories/health/html/2017/03/20170307_220138.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"2ce089771c1701b3bdc5263e1445a4b4ad525efd","tid":147440,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T00:02:39.000Z","msg":"快撚啲仙遊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}